abstract: This broadcast courtesy of Win 4 Wollongong shows the final of the Illawarra County Council and Shoalhaven Shire Council Bake-Off Competition 1968-69.
description: 1968-69 Illawarra County Council and Shoalhaven Shire Council Bake-Off Competition -  Broadcast 1968. Hosted by Alan Hoy, the final broadcast from Illawarra County Council show rooms in Burelli St, Wollongong. Contestants Mrs Nance, Mrs Graham, Mrs Boreham, Mrs Gosby, Marie Hoppo, Mrs Barra, Mrs Parsons, Mrs Nelson, Mrs Morrison, Mrs Glenn,  Mrs Nandall, Mrs Murphy, Mrs Petersen and Mrs Tiffen are interviewed as they're cooking.  Judges panel includes Mrs Ella Crawford, Shayne Wessell, Mrs Joan McPhail. Guest Stuart Wagstaff draws lucky door prizes for audience and announces the three major prize winners.
